{
  "stem": "22910.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She chose me to be the gatekeeper, which meant that when it was curfew, which was most of the time, really, if anybody had to go out, I should open the gate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then anybody who wanted to come to let them in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the toilet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Usually to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you couldn't confess you want a drink.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To toilet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for that I got-- I got an extra ration of soup, which was a-- a real important thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I got some things more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From Shlomo, as I said, I got some things, but certainly not to-- to have to my fill, certainly not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, we were there about nine weeks, which made that May, June-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] towards the end of July.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- of course, I forgot to mention the fact that they have all kinds of selections.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They selected-- meaning they had those zahlappells, which was the counting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then an important looking German, most the time it was Mengele, who came to see if there are anybody-- if there's anybody who doesn't look very strong and take out all the ones who weren't-- who looked very weak and just take them away.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after awhile, we began thinking this is last journey.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, at one point, they took out my sister, because she had swollen feet and she wasn't feeling so well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Boy, I-- it was just the most terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They kept them somewhere surrounded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow or other, I got her out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got her out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know what I would have done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, I got her out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So any time there was a selection, she wanted to stand behind me, because usually we faced the German, hoping he'll see me.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
